  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sant Gothard is on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner served in the hotels restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a continental buffet with hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Dinner is a three course buffet with a daily salad bar, starter, main and dessert options.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Sant Gothard is a great choice for a ski holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/07c4ee80b2bd4b5c9640b262a5748dd7}" title="Arinsal">Arinsal</a>. The rooms are modern and nicely furnished and offer fantastic views of the valley and resort. This hotel is a perfect choice is you are looking for a laid-back atmosphere for your ski trip. The ski bus stops directly outside the hotel to take you to the main gondola station, and on those slopes!</p>
<h2>Relax and recharge</h2>
<p>During your stay in the Sant Gothard, there'll be plenty of opportunities for you to take a moment to relax. There is a lovely relaxation area with a sauna and jacuzzi available for you to use for a local fee. Before dinner head to the bar for a drink, the lounge has plenty of seating so you can catch up with friends and chat about your day skiing.</p>
<h2>Great food </h2>
<p>The Sant Gothard Hotel has a modern restaurant that serves a delicious <span>buffet breakfast and three-course evening meal. There's also an on-site café to satisfy those snack cravings and h</span><span>ead over to the bar area to enjoy a drink in the cosy, communal lounge area with friends and family. </span></p>]]></description>
