  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sant Gothard offers excellent value for money with its comfortable atmosphere, good food, friendly service and high level of facilities. This hotel is offered on a half board basis so expect a stress free holiday with morning and evening meals included. Located in the heart of La Massana, this property is a great choice for those wanting easy access to the resort centre and gondola to the ski area.</p>]]></listingDescription>
