  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Double Bedrooms</strong> sleep two to three people with three twin beds. These rooms are located in block 1 and 3.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Double Bedrooms</strong> have been renovated in recent years, and sleep two to three people with three twin beds. These rooms are located in block 2. </p>
<p>Single rooms are available upon request.</p>
<p>Rooms allocated according to the number of people so two people may only receive a room with two beds. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds - please let us know your preference at the time of booking</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower or bath with showerhead attachment </li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Cots are available free of charge for babies, must be booked in advance </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
